                        <p style="margin: 0px;">As a leading hotel booking agency in Southeast Asia, since its launch, Hotel has made travel easier than ever for over 20 million travel enthusiasts. Not only operating in Southeast Asia, Hotel is currently a partner of over 200,000 hotels worldwide, always ready to accompany you anytime, anywhere.</p>
