                        <h4><strong>Integrated advanced features, booking a hotel on Hotel has never been easier</strong></h4>
                        <p style="margin: 0px;"><br></p>
                        <p style="margin: 0px;">Start by entering the destination in the "Search hotels" section, and hundreds of results will be displayed in a flash based on your preferences. The Hotel app will categorize the results into two segments – Budget and Premium, helping you quickly narrow down your options. Especially when selecting check-in dates, Hotel will notify you of the dates with the lowest prices. No need to compare back and forth; booking affordable hotels is now just a few steps away.</p>
                        <p style="margin: 0px;">All the most detailed information about hotels is constantly updated. Amenities, nearby areas, and reviews from previous guests will give you a comprehensive overview of the hotel you’re considering. The displayed price is also the final price you’ll pay, including taxes, with no hidden fees or extra charges. You only need one interface to compare many options and easily <strong>book affordable hotels</strong> with the best amenities.</p>
                        <p style="margin: 0px;">Frequent travelers, or those whose plans change unexpectedly, need not worry. The “Last-Minute Hotels” feature will be your savior. Hotel will filter out hotels with available rooms for the day at the best prices, sometimes with discounts of up to 50%, hard to find anywhere else.</p>
                        <p style="margin: 0px;">Once your booking is complete, all the details will be sent to your email and saved in the "My Bookings" section, helping you manage your transactions by date. Additionally, the hotel booking code details will include a translated address in the local language, a map, and a contact number, for cases where you’re traveling to countries where English is not spoken.</p>
